<font size=+1><b>Company Index</b><br>
</font>						<a href="#NYSE:WMT">Wal-Mart Stores, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:HD">The Home Depot, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:GM">General Motors Corporation</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:C">Chrysler Corporation</a><br>

					<p>

					<p>
	
		
