28. Associated Communications    <a name="NYSE:COA"></a><a href="http://www.hoovers.com/cgi-bin/brand_worth_mlist.cgi?mode=full&index_code=10356"><img src="/imgs/graph.gif" border=0><b>Coachmen Industries</b></a>
