					</pre>


					</font>
					<p>

<font size=+1><b>Company Index</b><br>
</font>						<a href="#NASD:CTLI">CTL Credit</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:WES">Westcorp </a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:BSC">The Bear Stearns Companies Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:VON">The Vons Companies, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:ABS">Albertson's, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NASD:NOBE">Nordstrom, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:DH">Dayton Hudson Corporation</a><br>

