		<title> Worth OnLine - 08/14/96 -- Samuel Stewart, founder and president of Wasatch Advisors Inc.</title>
	</head>
	
	<body background="/imgs/goldbarsmooth.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
	      text="#000000" link="#FF0000" vlink="#BB0000"> 	
