		<title> Worth OnLine - 06/18/96 -- Rudy Maxa (Savvy Traveler), author of "Europe When It Sizzles"</title>
	</head>
	
	<body background="/imgs/goldbarsmooth.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
