JSHDFR     : 
Are you into trading foreign markets as a whole? Is this a viable approach to going global?<p>
WorthJubak : 
JSHDFR, do you  mean trading in and out of countries? Or buying diversified funds?<p>
JSHDFR     : 
Buying diversified funds, thanks.<p>
WorthJubak : 
JSHDFR, I think of foreign investing like small cap US sector. Markets are inefficient. That means $. I like foreign funds where the managers work hard--Templeton, SoGen, for example.<p>
POOTERPUTT : 
