<center>[ <a href="http://www.worth.com/forums/talktoworth/lynch/worthboard.html">Return to the Front of this Board</a> ]</center>
<p>Message Posted by <p><a href="mailto:BPRG45A@PRODIGY.COM">Charles B. Walker</a> on August 25, 1996 at 08:34:55:<p>
   I have read all of your books, but<br>must say that I hope this one wil be part of a series.<br>   The style was very easy to read. No subject was drug out and the boy and girl examples were (especially with the cars) pure deja vu.<br>   Please let us know when your next book is coming and what it is about.<br>   Even my daughter reads them, althought she is a better investor then I am, because she gets it from me!<p>
